## Phoenix Omega (New Workflow)\
\
Phoenix Omega is a deterministic, substitution-only template workflow based on fixed 12 chapter templates and persona/topic variables (no prose generation).\
\
**Language Rule (Required):** Templates may describe past attempts to "fix, remove, eliminate, or get rid of" a state only in reflective or negated framing \'97 never as advice, instruction, or goal.\
