#### 1) Structural Integrity (CSV Shape)\
- Required columns: 
\f8\fs28 \cb10 chapter
\f0\fs32 \cb7 , 
\f8\fs28 \cb10 order
\f0\fs32 \cb7 , 
\f8\fs28 \cb10 section_key
