## System Integration & Architecture\
\
### Phase Dependencies\

\f8 Phase 1 (Protocol Slots) \uc0\u8592  Independent foundation\
Phase 2 (Structure Families) \uc0\u8592  Uses Phase 1, independent of Phase 3  \
Phase 3 (Modules) \uc0\u8592  Uses Phase 1+2, optional activation
\f0 \
\
### Data Flow\
1. **Book initialization** 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Load protocol slots, structure families, module policy\
2. **Planning phase** 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Apply protocol slots to topic context\
3. **Structure resolution** 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Select CSV based on structure family or fallback\
4. **Chapter assembly** 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Hydrate templates with all slots + optional modules\
5. **Manifest generation** 
\f4 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  Log all decisions for audit/traceability\
\
### Backward Compatibility\
- **Phase 1**: No impact when protocol CSV missing/empty\
- **Phase 2**: Persona heuristics as fallback, no family required\
- **Phase 3**: Off-by-default, no changes when 
\f8\fs28 \cb10 module_chapters=False
\f0\fs32 \cb7 \
